Discussion.S:
Previous studies have described nigral afferents from 
    the ipsilateral hypothalamus (Bunney and Aghajanian, '76; 
    Nauta and Domesick, '76).

It is significant that this same type of association is 
    seen in tectothalamocortical connections (Harting et al., '80; 
    Leichnetz et al., '81).

This nucleus also projects to the AId prefrontal cortex 
    and to the lateral precentral cortex (Krettek and Price, '77; 
    Gerfen and Clavier, '79).
